genius.core.events

Class SessionEndedNormallyEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • genius.core.events.SessionEndedNormallyEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NegotiationEvent, SessionEndedEvent

    public class SessionEndedNormallyEvent
extends java.lang.Object
implements SessionEndedEvent
    Abstract superclass indicating end of a session. All events happening after this event are for another session. This is not called if there is a SessionFailedEvent.
